<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to <%= appName %></title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { text-align: center; padding: 20px 0; }
        .logo { max-width: 150px; height: auto; }
        .verification-code {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 5px;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border: 1px dashed #ccc;
        }
        .footer { 
            margin-top: 30px; 
            padding-top: 20px; 
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .note {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to <%= appName %>!</h1>
        </div>
        
        <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
        
        <p>Thank you for joining <%= appName %>! We're excited to have you on board.</p>
        
        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <p>Your email verification code is:</p>
            <div class="verification-code"><%= code %></div>
            <p class="note">This code will expire in 30 minutes.</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>If you didn't request this code, please ignore this email or contact support if you have any concerns.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>The <%= appName %> Team</p>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= appName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="<%= frontendUrl %>/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> | 
                <a href="<%= frontendUrl %>/terms">Terms of Service</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
